blog.name: ethics-basket
blog.title: Ethics Basket: A Fruits Basket Blog
blog.description: This Blog focuses on the ethics in Natsuki Takaya's manga/anime Fruits Basket (Furuba). I also post and reblog the funny stuff :)

title: Reviewers you should watch
body:
If you guys aren’t already watching the youtubers JoJo Talks Too Much and AH Brandon Anime Reviews then you’re missing out. Both of these guys are completely new to the world of Fruits Basket and hearing their innocent perspectives and watching their thoughts on the series change with each episode really brings a breath of fresh air to the fandom. I just adore seeing a blossoming love for Fruits Basket take place before my eyes.

JoJo Talks Too Much‘s Deep Thoughts series on fruits basket is so enjoyable. Watching him talk about how certain scenes affect him just makes my day. Also he doesn’t have a lot of followers right now so please go check him out. I really want to help him out. (Also Shigure is his husbando)

AH Brandon Anime Reviews has a real knack for observation. His analyses of the show’s scenes lead to some very good guesses and sometimes he’s right on the mark. I love how detail oriented he is and I can’t wait for him to figure out more of the sohma’s secrets.

I’ve been watching these two newcomers review furuba for a while and can say that they are definitely a must-watch. Btw I don’t know these two in real life and they did not ask me to do this. They do not know I exist. I really just think you should watch them.
